<li><strong>Balanced Diet: </strong>The proper dietary intake of fruits, vegetables, whole grain products, lean meats, proteins, and healthy fats fosters nutritional and energy reinforcement, as well as a more stable mood. A balanced diet can also contribute to improved cognition and help to decrease anxiety and or depression.</li>



