<li><strong><a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/bryonia-alba-uses"   title="Bryonia Alba" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked"  data-wpil-monitor-id="2600">Bryonia Alba</a>:</strong> Indicated for exercise-stimulated chest pain or pains that are intensified by deep breathing as it relates to inflammation.</li>



