<li><strong>Kali Carb:</strong> Useful in acute respiratory exacerbations, particularly if the patient has excessive chest phlegm and sharp chest pain on taking very shallow breaths.</li>



<li><strong><a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/hepar-sulphur-uses"   title="Hepar Sulphur" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked"  data-wpil-monitor-id="2100">Hepar Sulphur</a>:</strong> It is perfect for conditions where there is pus-like sputum production, decreasing mucus and lessening inflammation in the lungs.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Best Homeopathic Remedies for Pneumonia</h2>



