<li><strong>Avoid Contaminated Water:</strong> It is recommended to take only clean water without bacteria or to boil or take filtered water to avoid re-infection.</li>



<li><strong>Follow Medical Treatment:</strong> Take antibiotics and all other prescriptions as directed by the physician to the letter. The successful treatment of this bacteria requires the taking of the full course, since missing some tablets will leave the bacteria in the system.</li>



