<p>Homeopathy can be a complementary therapy for dengue Shock Syndrome, helping to alleviate symptoms and support healing. Common remedies include <a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/eupatorium-perfoliatum-uses" title="Eupatorium Perfoliatum" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked" data-wpil-monitor-id="2567">Eupatorium Perfoliatum</a> for fever, Gelsemium as a sedative, and Bryonia as a muscle relaxant. While homeopathic treatment for dengue Shock Syndrome does not treat the virus itself, it may enhance immunity and recovery.</p>



